priority-signs.title: Stop
priority-signs.desc: It is mandatory to stop completely at the stop line, or if not available, as close to the crossing road or railway track as possible, before continuing. Vehicles must also give way to other traffic, or trains.

priority-signs.title: Priority road
priority-signs.desc: Priority at all following crossroads up to an end of priority road, give way or stop sign.

priority-signs.title: Priority crossroads
priority-signs.desc: Warns about dangerous crossroads where the road this sign is placed on has priority. Crossing roads have give way or stop signs.
